::Striker::

Striker raises his eyebrow as Sniper tells him to go give the new bot 
quarters. He wasn't used to being told what to do by an inferior officer. 
Either way, though, it was a good idea. "Follow me," he says to Pegasus and 
walks off down a hallway.
